   Boards & Commissions

   In addition to the support of its 14 departments, Business,
   Transportation & Housing Agency is an active member of boards and
   commissions. The purpose is to delve deeper into issues that will make
   communities safe, sustainable, and economically vital now and into the
   future.

   Here are boards and commissions that Business, Transportation & Housing
   Agency supports:
     * New Motor Vehicle Board
     * The Commission on Building for the 21st Century
     * California Workforce Investment Board
     * California Census

